Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.190 --> 00:00:04.320
In the first phase of this course, you learned about object oriented analysis,

00:00:04.320 --> 00:00:07.840
in which you searched for various categories of words, nouns, verbs,

00:00:07.840 --> 00:00:11.320
adjectives, in the textural description of the system you were building.

00:00:11.320 --> 00:00:15.680
Martin contrasts this approach to one in which behavior is central.

00:00:15.680 --> 00:00:17.810
We will look at both, beginning with OOA.

